-size: 14px\">城镇职工基本医疗保险住院手续办理流程</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 34pt\">\r\n            <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 30.84%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 34pt; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">政策法规依据</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"69%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: #ece9d8; width: 69.16%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 34pt; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">嘉鱼县城镇职工基本医疗保险实施细则（嘉政发[2010]6号</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 34pt\">\r\n            <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 30.84%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 34pt; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">事项申办条件</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"69%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: #ece9d8; width: 69.16%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 34pt; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">由参保职工个人申报</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 30.84%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">申报材料</span></span></div>\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"69%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: #ece9d8; width: 69.16%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">一、本人医保证、定点医院的初次诊断病历、相关疾病检查报告单、住院审批表；</span></span></div>\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">二、IC卡、住（转）院审批表(异地就医登记表)、出院小结、住院费用清单、医院费用有效票据</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 30.84%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">办事处理流程</span></span></div>\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"69%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: #ece9d8; width: 69.16%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">一、参保职工住院必须到县内定点医院就诊，请携带本人医保证、凭定点医院的初次诊断病历、相关疾病检查报告单、住院审批表，到医保中心审核批准。急诊可先入院，在三日内补办相关手续。未经医保中心审批所发生的医疗费用不予支付</span></span></div>\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">二、职工医疗保险实行定点逐级转院制度，本地定点医疗机构确因技术和设备条件所限不能诊治的疾病，由县人民医院出具《病情诊断证明》并填写转院审批表、科室主任签署意见、医保科复审并加盖公章，经医保中心审批后，携带本人医保证、转院审批表、转院介绍信到上级定点医院办理登记手续。危重、抢救病人先转后批，三日内补办相关手续。转院期间的医疗费用，先由本人垫付。</span></span></div>\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">三、异地居住人员（异地投亲、回原籍居住一年以上的退休人员）须办理异地就医登记备案手续。经本人申请，医疗保险经办机构同意，填写《咸宁市城镇职工基本医疗保险异地居住人员登记表》，住院3日内须电话申报住院时间、医院名称、住院病种；并将入院证、疾病诊断证明书传真至医保中心备案。住院医疗费当年审核报销 (跨年度住院的情形例外)，住院未申报所发生的费用不予报销。驻外机构人员就医参照本规定执行。</span></span></div>\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">四、因公外出就医。参保人员因公出差、学习、探亲期间患急症需就诊或住院治疗的，须在当地定点医疗机构就医，并在3&mdash;5日内到参保地医疗保险经办机构办理登记手续，待病情稳定后回参保地定点医疗机构治疗；外地治疗期间费用由本人或单位垫付，出院后次月到参保地医疗保险经办机构审核报销。</span></span></div>\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">五、住院费用结算需提供本人医保证和IC卡、住（转）院审批表(异地就医登记表)、出院小结、住院费用清单、医院费用有效票据， </span></span></div>\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 30.84%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">办理时限</span></span></div>\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"69%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: #ece9d8; width: 69.16%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">一、县内出院时合规医疗费在定点医院刷卡结算，个人负担部份在预交金扣除，多退少补；投保单位欠费和超过基本医疗最高支付限额的，出院时全额垫付住院费用，待单位缴清欠费和大额医疗保险赔付后，再到定点医院结算住院费用；</span></span></div>\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">二、转诊到省内其它定点医院的住院费用由个人全额垫付，出院后与医保中心直接结算（异地居住患者一日内办结，其它患者七日内办结）。</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 34pt\">\r\n            <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 30.84%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 34pt; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">收费标准</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"69%\" style=\"border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: #ece9d8; width: 69.16%; padding-top: 0cm; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; height: 34pt; background-color: transparent\">\r\n            <div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">不收费</span></span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('967','6','雷明清、李红梅','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-11-25/539a751ef954abdfc53015c533cc43b7.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">全省地税系统企业所得税座谈会会场</span></div>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"11\\\\\" day=\\\\\"24\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>日</st1:chsdate>，全省地税系统企业所得税管理工作座谈会在嘉鱼召开。省地税局税政二处处长雷浩主持会议，全省各市、州地税局代表参加了此次会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">会上，各市、州局与会代表们详细汇报了各地企业所得税管理工作情况，省局税政二处副处长余永红讲解了企业所得税征管范围政策及具体要求，对高新技术企业认定工作情况进行了通报，指出了我省企业所得税管理工作中存在的问题<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>并及时谋划了整改措施。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">雷浩在会上充分肯定全省各地企业所得税管理工作<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>要求各地加大工作力度<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>进一步推进企业所得税管理<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>并对全省地税系统下阶段企业所得税管理工作进行了安排部署。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">咸宁市地税局副局长李相忠参加了此次会议。</span></p>\r\n</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('968','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-11-25/457ab935c5ebb8d482a6afba4596c252.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂在会上讲话<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"11\\\\\" day=\\\\\"25\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，嘉鱼县召开</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度党报党刊发行工作会。县长余珂要求各镇各单位切实增强做好重点党报党刊发行工作的责任感和使命感；突出重点，强化措施，确保党报党刊征订工作顺利进行；加强组织领导，强化工作督查，确保我县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度党报党刊发行工作任务圆满完成。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记李国光，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权，县委办主任章斌出席会议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议指出，各级党组织、各企事业单位、机关、团体、学校、社区、行政村及干部职工都要积极订阅党报党刊，城镇每个党支部至少要订阅</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">份《人民日报》、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">份《求是》、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">份《湖北日报》、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">份《咸宁日报》。特别是《咸宁日报》的发行要切实做到：机关到科室，商贸到门店，厂矿企业到车间，宾馆到房间，学校到班级。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议要求，各镇各单位要划定党报党刊订阅的专项经费，各级共青团、工会要拿出一定数量的团费、工会会费订阅党报党刊。农村每个行政村按照人平不超过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">元限额用公费合理安排订阅党报，所需经费由财政统一转移支付。鼓励自费订阅，特别是各级领导干部要带头自费订阅党报党刊。各镇要在镇区人口相对集中的地段设置户外公共阅报栏，张贴三级党报。县内大型宾馆、主要休闲场所、客运站、银行、机构办事大厅等流动人员较多的场所要设置阅报点，配齐三级党报和读报必备条件，不断壮大党报党刊的读者群。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委宣传部、财政局、邮政局纷纷表示将为各单位报刊发行工作做好服务，确保党报党刊发行任务圆满完成。目前，我县正在掀起一股积极征订党报党刊的热潮。会议结束后，各镇各单位纷纷主动与邮政部门联系，已有六个镇全面完成发行任务。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，从</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日起，我县将每天通报一次各镇、各单位党报党刊的征订进度，对征订工作完成不够好的单位进行专项督办，力争在</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日前完成任务。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-11-25/b1ebb84d2ce901df5d2bd4624956346a.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议现场</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
